    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <h2>Security Considerations</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>All traffic is encrypted end-to-end through Cloudflare's network.</li>
    <li>The authentication token is required for all API requests and dashboard access.</li>
    <li>The same token guards local and remote requests; rotate it by deleting <code>tokenSecret</code> from <code>~/.band/settings.json</code> and restarting the server.</li>
    <li>The tunnel can be stopped at any time to immediately revoke remote access.</li>
    <li>No ports are opened on your local firewall.</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
